race.comment: SET TO SIZZLE (4) scored two back then well held latest finishing a 26 length 7th at The Meadows (36.17). Has won two of three starts from this draw. Can discover winning form. GOLD CLASS COOL (7) has a strong overall record having six wins and 10 places from 24 starts but was out of the money last time when fourth (25.45) over 450m at Shepparton. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Expected to feature on best form. MEPUNGA BROCKIE (3) goes very well at this course having never missed the frame including four wins. Missed the frame latest (30.65) when fourth over 525m at The Meadows in a Special conditions SF. Can hit the frame with the right run. ZINGING HOT (1) showed plenty of dash to record a last start win. Hard to beat again.
